    • build

      public net.minecraft.core.Holder<net.minecraft.world.level.dimension.DimensionType> build()
      Builds the DimensionType. This method returns an intrusive holder that must be properly added the registry. RegistryProviderBase does this automatically if the result is stored in a public, non-static field inside the provider.
